To compile all plugins you need:

- automake 1.7 or better
- libtool 1.4e or better

- glib 2.2.0 (http://www.gtk.org/)
- gtk+ 2.2.0 (http://www.gtk.org/) - GUI
- libgadu 1.3.1 or newer (http://dev.null.pl/ekg/) - Gadu-Gadu
- libtlen (http://www.libtlen.eu.org) - Tlen
- Loudmouth 0.15.1 or newer (http://www.imendio.com/projects/loudmouth/) - Jabber
- xosd (http://ignavus.net/software.html) - XOSD
- esound (http://www.tux.org/~ricdude/EsounD.html - sound-esd

WARNING: perl support and remote plugin will compile/work only on Linux!

Read doc/problems and other documentation files BEFORE submitting ANY
bugreports.

Important :

    If you accidentally will make something wrong with list of plugins to be loaded,
    you can remove file $HOME/.gg2/modules.load and start GNU Gadu that will load all available plugins.